<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC56A7AFF55972A1DCCBA8E" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC56A7AFF55972A1DCCBA8E" blockId="62.[167,1374,292,881]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFC56A7AFF55972A1F17BAA6" bold="true" box="[169,279,371,404]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Habitat.</emphasis>
The Isalo Serotine has been netted foraging over water in transitional gallery tropical dry forest in canyons, at elevations of 450-700 m.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC56A7AFF55979A1C9DBAD6" box="[169,669,451,484]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC56A7AFF55979A1C9DBAD6" blockId="62.[167,1374,292,881]" box="[169,669,451,484]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFC56A7AFF55979A1FAEBAD6" bold="true" box="[169,430,451,484]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC56A7AFF5597B31ADBB900" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" type="breeding">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC56A7AFF5597B31ADBB900" blockId="62.[167,1374,292,881]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFC56A7AFF5597B31F2FB939" bold="true" box="[169,303,490,523]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Breeding.</emphasis>
In Isalo National Park, a male captured in December had slightly enlarged testes, and a female had large mammae, indicating recently ceased lactation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC56A7AFF5B94611B16B9B3" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" type="activity">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC56A7AFF5B94611B16B9B3" blockId="62.[167,1374,292,881]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFC56A7AFF5B94611F91B96B" bold="true" box="[167,401,568,601]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Based on calls ofsix individuals, FM/QCF components are produced at low-duty cycle, with maximum energy in fundamental harmonic at ¢.45-8 kHz.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC56A7AFF5594D11A54B99B" box="[169,1108,648,681]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" type="biology_ecology">
