No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC56A7AFF5694F61C29B812" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC56A7AFF5694F61C29B812" blockId="62.[167,1374,292,881]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFC56A7AFF5694F61C04B9E2" bold="true" box="[170,516,687,720]" pageId="62" pageNumber="820">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. The Isalo Serotine is only known from a few specimens. It occurs in Isalo National Park, occupying a restricted area of 
<quantity id="036C9B1BFFC56A7AFE5F94A61C1CB812" box="[419,540,767,800]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.905" pageId="62" pageNumber="820" unit="km" value="1905.0">1905 km</quantity>
²
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
